<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover">
    <title>Contact Us - Two Dee Engineering</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #ffffff 50%, #f1f5f9 100%); color: #0f172a; }
        
        .nav-card {
            position: fixed;
            top: 20px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.98);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border-radius: 50px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(44,94,46,0.15);
            padding: 8px 20px;
            z-index: 1000;
            width: auto;
            max-width: 90%;
        }
        .nav-container { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
        .nav-link { padding: 8px 16px; color: #334155; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; border-radius: 40px; white-space: nowrap; transition: all 0.3s; }
        .nav-link:hover { background: rgba(44,94,46,0.1); color: #2C5E2E; }
        .admin-link { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2C5E2E, #800020); color: white !important; }
        .admin-link:hover { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3D7A3F, #A00028); transform: translateY(-1px); }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .nav-card { width: 94%; border-radius: 30px; padding: 10px 16px; top: 15px; }
            .nav-link { padding: 6px 12px; font-size: 13px; }
        }
        
        .container { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 140px 40px 80px; }
        .page-title { text-align: center; font-size: 48px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 20px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a, #2C5E2E); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; }
        .subtitle { text-align: center; color: #64748b; margin-bottom: 50px; font-size: 18px; }
        .contact-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 40px; }
        .info-card, .form-card { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); padding: 35px; border-radius: 24px; border: 1px solid rgba(44,94,46,0.1); transition: all 0.3s; }
        .info-card:hover, .form-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.95); }
        .info-card h3, .form-card h3 { color: #2C5E2E; margin-bottom: 25px; font-size: 24px; }
        .info-detail { margin-bottom: 25px; }
        .info-detail strong { display: block; margin-bottom: 8px; color: #0f172a; }
        .info-detail p { color: #64748b; }
        .form-group { margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .form-group label { display: block; margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 500; color: #334155; }
        .form-group input, .form-group textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 14px;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 16px;
            font-family: inherit;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            background: #f8fafc;
        }
        .form-group input:focus, .form-group textarea:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #2C5E2E;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(44,94,46,0.1);
            background: white;
        }
        .submit-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2C5E2E, #800020);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 14px 30px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            width: 100%;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        .submit-btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(44,94,46,0.3); }
        .footer { background: #0f172a; color: white; padding: 60px 40px 30px; margin-top: 60px; text-align: center; }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container { padding: 180px 20px 60px; }
            .page-title { font-size: 32px; }
            .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="nav-card">
        <div class="nav-container">
            <a href="/" class="nav-link">Home</a>
            <a href="/services" class="nav-link">Services</a>
            <a href="/projects" class="nav-link">Projects</a>
            <a href="/about" class="nav-link">About</a>
            <a href="/contact" class="nav-link">Contact</a>
            <a href="/admin/login" class="nav-link admin-link">🔐 Admin</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="page-title">Contact Us</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Ready to discuss your next project? Let's talk.</p>
        <div class="contact-grid">
            <div class="info-card">
                <h3>📍 Get in Touch</h3>
                <div class="info-detail"><strong>Office Address</strong><p>No 139, Murtala Muhammad Way<br>Kano State, Nigeria</p></div>
                <div class="info-detail"><strong>Phone</strong><p>(+234) 08123216050</p></div>
                <div class="info-detail"><strong>Email</strong><p>twodeeengineer</p></div>
                <div class="info-detail"><strong>Business Hours</strong><p>Monday - Friday: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM</p></div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-card">
                <h3>Send a Message</h3>
                <form action="/contact/submit" method="POST">
                    <div class="form-group"><label>Your Name *</label><input type="text" name="name" required></div>
                    <div class="form-group"><label>Email Address *</label><input type="email" name="email" required></div>
                    <div class="form-group"><label>Message *</label><textarea name="message" rows="5" required></textarea></div>
                    <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">Send Message →</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <footer class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2011 Two Dee Engineering Services. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p style="margin-top: 10px; font-size: 12px;">Licensed PE: TX-123456 | CA-789101</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
